data.description: Great Milwood Location close to everything Kalamazoo! This Gorgeous home features large spaces with a mix of traditional charm and modern touches including newer windows, hardwood floors, and an open concept! The main floor features 2 living rooms each with their own fireplace and lots of natural light, a well placed  1/2 bath,  separate dining area (could be a main floor office and currently used as a main floor bedroom) recently remodeled kitchen with beautiful butcher block counters and tons of prep space for anyone who loves cooking.  The back living room is incredibly large and has gorgeous wooden ceilings.  Upstairs you will find 3 good sized bedrooms and a full bath.  Bonus rec room in the basement with another fireplace. You'll love everything from the deck in the back to the bonus room down in the basement as this is just a truly well designed house.  Newer Roof, Furnace, and water heater and all the appliances are included.
